▪️Newcomer of the Year: Jacob Shaffelburg

▪️Humanitarian of the Year: Taylor Washington

▪️Academy Player of the Year: Adem Sipić

▪️Huntsville City FC Player of the Year: Kemy Amiche

▪️Employee of the Year: Jeff Robben & Lindsey Fungfeld

▪️Rookie Employee of the Year: Sam Joyce & Liv Ungurean

More than a game.

Nashville SC fan Max recently lost his collection of NSC memorabilia in an apartment fire, including a signed jersey from Dan Lovitz. At our Leagues Cup Final on Saturday, @ilovitz11 brought Max a brand new signed jersey, and Max joined us on the field for our pre-match ceremonies. Shoutout to the NSC community for rallying behind Max and his father to help create a special moment. We 🫶 you, Max
